      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a machine with stories in its metal and plenty of life left for the next owner with a little vision. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone seeking budget-friendly wheels, a hands-on project, or a dependable companion to shape into something uniquely their own. There\u2019s a gritty charm here you just don\u2019t get from newer, cookie-cutter options, and at this price, it opens the door to possibility without asking for a fortune.",
