      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking reliable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows the signs of age you would expect, but it remains a sensible choice for someone who values utility, low upfront cost, and honest ownership. A great fit for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels.",
