      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without any fuss. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a straightforward budget-friendly option with plenty of potential for a handy buyer, commuter, or spare runabout. If you\u2019re after cheap transport and know how to appreciate a car with a bit of character, this one could be a great fit.",
